LOVE ME LITTLE, LOVE ME LONG
Love me little love me long,
love me till the morning dawns.
Love me little love me long,
Love me till the moon goes down.
Love me little love me long.
Love me little love me long.
Love me little love me long,
love me when the rain pours down.
Love me little love me long,
love me when the wind blows hard.
Love me little love me long.
Love me little love me long.
Love me little love me long,
love me through all the pain.
Love me little love me long,
love me through the blue bird's song.
Love me little love me long.
Love me little love me long.
12/20/13

